<p>Potential energy is easier to go straight to from polar coordinates:</p>

<span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>U</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>âˆ’</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>g</mi><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>cos</mi><mo>â¡</mo><msub><mi>Î¸</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>âˆ’</mo><msub><mi>m</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>cos</mi><mo>â¡</mo><msub><mi>Î¸</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>cos</mi><mo>â¡</mo><msub><mi>Î¸</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U = -m_1gl_1\cos\theta_1 - m_2g(l_1\cos\theta_1 + l_2\cos\theta_2)\\</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">âˆ’</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">m</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">â€‹</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="msupsub"><